               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the donor (only the second component); elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
Several groups of lines on the incipit page of Text I, alternating with black lines; groups of lines in the incipit of Text I-2, alternating with black lines; one to three initial lines in the incipit of Texts I-3 to I-8; initial lines or initial word in the incipit of the sections of the daily readings (homilies, absolution prayers, miracles and ʾarke); initial line in the incipit of Text II; first word of each stanza.</rubric>
